{"tid":2165624,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Joy@Red Velvet着撐女權Tee惹爭議","createTime":"2020-08-20T02:57:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-20T04:45:54.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"442993d7dd04b25299ddc44ad72e0fb39ced7d3a","tid":2165624,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:57:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20200820/photo/bkn-20200820103504803-0820_00862_001_01p.jpg?20200820103511\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20200820%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20200820103504803-0820_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20200820103511&h=ce1f855a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓團Red Velvet成員Wendy於去年12月25日綵排《SBS歌謠大戰》期間，由2.5米高舞台墮下，身上多處骨折，經過8個月的休養後，她終於相隔8個月歸隊，與隊友一起翻唱同門師姐BoA的《Milky Way》，慶祝BoA出道20周年，事務所今日公開5位成員合體拍攝的宣傳照。<br />\n<br />\n而隊友Seulgi與Joy昨日出席國家氣候環境會主辦的「藍天之日」宣傳大使委任儀式，Joy其後在社交網上傳身穿印上支持女權主義「We Should All Be Feminists」的Tee，惹起爭議。"},{"pid":"72898d6e11d2982b55bfa1080ca22f94e36ebf28","tid":2165624,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T02:58:52.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"c1276c4fa55f9174d1b42fd50fa4be2b0bf0f8d3","tid":2165624,"uid":117802,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:26:47.000Z","msg":"有咩爭議"},{"pid":"7453338391ad20bc3f09f28d561cda264e98389f","tid":2165624,"uid":71107,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"係韓國，講女權同其他地方講女權係2回事黎 (好似係)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uz_GVpBFa6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Duz_GVpBFa6k&d=MESMej01p5OZpZHaxDRuffYtrFBHe52Fn%2F6n3rMGN5k%3D&h=5666fcd3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uz_GVpBFa6k</a>"},{"pid":"cb909c57d7b5b41f242d73a357a1bc71bff6ef98","tid":2165624,"uid":208486,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T03:31:37.000Z","msg":"有咩問題?"},{"pid"